    <item>
      <title>最高法院维护与生俱来的公民权，阻止特朗普的一项关键政策</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/30/us/politics/supreme-court-birthright-citizenship.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法官们否决了特朗普总统的行政命令，该命令禁止无证移民和一些临时外国游客的子女获得与生俱来的公民身份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/30/us/politics/supreme-court-birthright-citizenship.html</guid>
